BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:0da00c88b6ab60ac@swarthmore-dash-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260603T154903Z
DTSTART:20260604T153000Z
DTEND:20260604T173000Z
SUMMARY:Garnet Day
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ["President's Office"]\\nCategory: Reception\\nDe
 ar Friends\, Join friends and colleagues in celebrating the end of another
  semester together! Stop by Old Science Lawn and the Rose Garden this Thur
 sday for a tasty lunch\, fun lawn games\, music\, and more. Enjoy a menu o
 f classic summer favorites — including fried chicken\, pulled pork\, hot
  dogs\, and mac and cheese — as well as vegan\, vegetarian\, and gluten-
 free options. There will be a selection of cobblers and pies for dessert.G
 arnet Day Staff Celebration Lunch Thursday\, June 4 11:30 a.m. – 1:30 
 p.m. Old Science Lawn Rain location: Singer Hall\, Singer Commons & Singer
  034/035By popular demand\, festivities will again include a corn hole tou
 rnament\, organized by the President’s Staff Advisory Council! The tour
 nament will start at noon\, and include both “just for fun” and “var
 sity” leagues. Teams of two can sign up here by Monday\, June 1. Ple
 ase reach out to psac@swarthmore.edu with any questions. As always\, rem
 ember to wear your Swarthmore gear to show your spirit!\\nDetails: https:/
 /swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D12811629
 95
LOCATION:Old Science Hall Lawn
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1281162995
CATEGORIES:Reception
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
