DTSTART:20260604T161500Z
DTEND:20260604T170000Z
SUMMARY:Group Circuit Training with Chris
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Recreation & Wellness']\\nCategory: Recreation-
 General\\nDo you struggle to figure out which workout to do at the gym\, o
 r do you need some extra motivation? If so\, this class is for you. Receiv
 e personal attention to help you improve your overall fitness through a to
 tal body workout. The class will offer modifications or challenges to suit
  each participant. Missed a workout? Review past workouts online. \\nDetai
 ls: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid
 %3D1381777501
LOCATION:Matchbox Lower Level Lewis Reynolds Performance Center
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1381777501
CATEGORIES:Recreation-General
END:VEVENT
