DTSTAMP:20260603T154903Z
DTSTART:20260610T010000Z
DTEND:20260610T020000Z
SUMMARY:Peter van de Kamp Observatory Open House
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Physics and Astronomy']\\nCategory: Open House\
 \nThe Physics and Astronomy department hosts a telescope open house on the
  second Tuesday of each month at the Peter van de Kamp Observatory on the 
 roof of the Science Center. Directions are available at www.swarthmore.edu
 /peter-van-de-kamp-observatory/directions. The open house hours are 8:00 p
 .m. to 9:00 p.m. during standard time and 9:00 p.m. to 10:00 p.m. during d
 aylight savings time. The SC-1 exterior door under the breezeway will be o
 pen 10 minutes before the start time. The rooftop access door will open at
  the event start time. If the weather is bad\, the open house will be canc
 elled by 5:00 p.m.\, and an announcement will be posted on the Physics and
  Astronomy department website and the College calendar. Check https://www
 .swarthmore.edu/physics-astronomy on the day of the open house if the weat
 her is questionable Open to the public. \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.s
 warthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1364584547
LOCATION:Science Center Peter Van de Kamp Observatory\, Science Center Obse
 rvatory Computer Room
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1364584547
CATEGORIES:Open House
END:VEVENT
