SUMMARY:Summer 2026 Workshop Series: Telling your story
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ["Provost's Office"\, 'Beyond The Classroom'\, 'D
 ivision of Student Affairs']\\nCategory: Lecture/Panel Discussion\\nTuesda
 ys and Thursdays in Sci 101 from 12-1:30pm. Lunch will be provided. Now th
 at you’re coming to the end of the summer program\, this workshop will h
 elp you reflect upon the skills you’ve gained and how far you’ve come.
  We’ll explore how your experiences shape your self-understanding and ho
 w to integrate new skills into your personal narrative(s). Finally\, we’
 ll consider how this reflection enables you to share your story impactfull
 y as you take your next steps. Presented by Susannah Fishman\, Director\, 
 Center for Innovation & Leadership\, and Rebecca Weintraub-Barth\, Directo
 r of Student Activities & Leadership.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swart
 hmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1395671886
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1395671886
